text: Altencelle is part of the borough of Celle in Lower Saxony and is southeast of the town centre, west of the River Aller and east of the Fuhse. It is linked to Celle by the B 214 federal road and state highway K 74. ==References== == Other websites == * The official website of Celle town Category:Villages in Lower Saxony Category:Celle
